{"type": "article", "id": 32416, "title": "没有抢到混凝草音乐节门票？现场曝光看这里！", "description": "“就算大雨让这座城市颠倒，我会给你怀抱”挡不住的热情，一场风雨已经悄然裹挟着混凝草音乐节上躁动的音乐狂人们震撼登陆上海。", "date": "2016-09-20T12:10:45Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 10, "author": 18, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160920201144xnPRrAuBUKSzypQI.jpeg", "contents": "<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920201332q7CO9hmVajnYsLXQ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.493716\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p align=\"left\">混凝草音乐节作为业内专业的团队，坚持以“前瞻性”的眼光，刻画着以“吸纳海外新鲜音乐及稀缺生活方式”的优质亚文化版图而在国内音乐节中独树一帜。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920201355IUvu3qxMOXfE4Heh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">无论是从舞台设计到灯光音效，还是从现场气氛到活动内容。都体现出不同于以往国内音乐节的精彩。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920201423RZfjlT8IKwxiUmeb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664502\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p align=\"left\">所有的演出嘉宾均来自各国电子、摇滚、和嘻哈音乐领域里的顶尖人物。其中包括,美国实力嘻哈团体A$AP Mob、缔造奇幻梦境的日本摇滚天团Sekai No Owari、令人热血沸腾的英伦独立摇滚乐队The Cribs，韩国嘻哈界的鼻祖Drunken Tiger以及身兼Rapper与韩剧歌后的尹美莱，以及陈冠希&amp;4PK。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920201442PYOS5C3M0uoajm74.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920201501kRDYldinBEbpmIA4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609202015184PAsD7y1RZYgXwNo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p align=\"left\">这些来自异度空间的电子乐、华丽的日式摇滚、纯正的英式独立、融会贯通的世界音乐等多元的类型，就此搭建起了一份自由年轻的音乐绿洲。</p><p align=\"left\">除了有好歌声，音乐节路人的时髦指数一点都不逊色于秀场外的街拍！</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003156zZSVAtYIicLBTfva.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501002\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920201603E4NDUky3OwXt5WzF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.359477\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003204JP6kFYfKw7l9UABG.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.503018\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016092020164053HbvEMFWg8BJys2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.504886\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003211SnyjfI05e7a9F4pw.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.513131\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p align=\"left\">此次尚品网携手TOPSHOP/TOPMAN联合赞助混凝草音乐节，除了令人激动的演出嘉宾阵容以外，还有充满时尚、新奇、热闹的创意车库。为音乐的弄潮儿们开辟了很多特别专区，加入了不一样的主题与惊喜,呈现出更多新鲜好玩的互动内容。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920201733enEsRM0i1VJoLO58.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664502\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p align=\"left\">那些现下火热的横须贺刺绣夹克、灵动飘逸的金属感百褶裙、革新经典的丹宁系列、和英伦范儿十足的印花风，都是音乐节夺人眼球的法宝穿搭元素。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016092020174882PGWtqhHliQEjxk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: center;\">TOPSHOP 刺绣夹克（尚品网有售）</p></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920201829VQRZfinOv0sb7czh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: center;\">TOPSHOP 百褶裙（尚品网有售）</p></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920201906HZnREKxl5WVOSD80.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: center;\">TOPSHOP 牛仔外套（尚品网有售）</p></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609202019559U8Zt3iVGgNMsHIO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: center;\">TOPSHOP 连身裙（尚品网有售）</p></figcaption></figure></div><p align=\"left\">音乐节除了享受音乐，纵情吃喝之外，扮美秀美也是音乐节文化非常重要的一个部分。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609202020353SeY2haNpu8qbrVU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664502\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p align=\"left\">就在尚品网TOPSHOP/TOPMAN 创意车库里，我们邀请到Andy Creation工作室的发型师、化妆师和造型师们让大家可以更直接地感受到音乐节文化。 一些幸运的乐迷朋友、和潮人也因此有机会体验到了一次不一样的造型设计。 搞怪可爱的纹身贴纸、色彩出挑的彩妆、个性爆棚的发型和夸张的配饰，全方位的打造出当下最时髦的音乐节专属造型。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920202055JAtDGSksrajL37EK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664502\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920202102e2KlTShvRQF1ot7L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664502\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920202117h7Ze62jTXzuBSvO3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p align=\"left\">打扮的美美的不留个纪念怎么行。我们引进了摄影大师Helmut Newton开发的创意自拍空间。解放了大家的双手，让自拍不在局限于磨皮瘦脸的大头照，而是更加展示自己的机会，秀出你的造型，突出你的潮流品味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920202132CYmoPk4DSqJwtunb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920202143oO9wAVYKtSG18Bku.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920202156U1s2D9pezmWaZdVN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920202233K89cPMp1oi4ywkRI.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}